snippet.title: Warframe | Heart of Deimos Update Trailer - Available now on all platforms!
snippet.description: Delve deep into the Heart of Deimos. Command your Necramech through a grotesque landscape teeming with Infested creatures. Learn the truth behind Deimos' dark inhabitants, the Entrati, and work with them to defend Deimos from the spreading Infestation. Get full info on Heart of Deimos: http://wrfr.me/deimos
